<author>frḥạn ạlʿbd, bhjt ʿdly</author>
<title>ydk ạlmtẖqwbẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ydk ạlmtẖqwbẗ rby tsbyny
 tsẖʿl fy ạ̉sẖwạqy wḥnyny
 wtdẖkrny bạ̉nk fy ywmiⁿ
 mn ạ̉jly qạsyt lky lạ tsẖqyny)2
 1- wkẖlạṣy mn ạlmwt lsbbiⁿ .. ạ̉nk ḍḥyt ky mạ tnjyny
 (lm ytẖnk mwtuⁿ ạ̉w ạ̉lmuⁿ .. knt msẖgẖwlaⁿạ bạ̉nyny
 lm yrhbk hwl ạlʿạr .. mjrwḥu ḥty̱ tsẖfyny)2
 2- lm yrḍk ạ̉n ạ̉bqy̱ ḥzynaⁿạ .. ạ̉ḥbbtny rby qbl ạltkwyn
 (ạ̉tbʿk rby wmsyḥy .. ạ̉nt mʿtqdy wdyny
 ạ̉ʿsẖqk ạ̉nt wydyk .. fy kfk rby kẖbyny)2

[V2]
 lm ytẖnk mwtuⁿ ạ̉w ạ̉lmuⁿ .. knt msẖgẖwlaⁿạ bạ̉nyny
 lm yrhbk hwl ạlʿạr .. mjrwḥuⁿ ḥty̱ tsẖfyny
 ạ̉tbʿk rby wmsyḥy .. ạ̉nt mʿtqdy wdyny
 ạ̉ʿsẖqk ạ̉nt wydyk .. fy kfk rby kẖbyny</lyrics>
</song>